lipsync
an open source linux application that provides a command-line, Dropbox-like service, using OpenSSH, rsync and lsyncd 

REQUIREMENTS
------------
	* Linux
	* OpenSSH
	* lsyncd
	* rsync

INSTALL
-------
Deian/Ubuntu
	# cd lipsync
	# chmod +x setup
	# ./setup.sh

BACKSTORY
---------
This is a realization of a popular blog post I made last year: 
	http://fak3r.com/2009/09/14/howto-build-your-own-open-source-dropbox-clone/

